# Operators · Atomic — XOR subgroup placeholder

The atomic (Z/2)ⁿ XOR-mask operators (imprint / project / flipᵢ /
hexCuo etc.) are defined on the Yi-flavored R₇/R₈ carriers in
`Foundation/Bagua/R7.lean` and `Foundation/Bagua/R8.lean`.  They are
involutions and pairwise commute, forming an abelian subgroup of the
full automorphism group of each R-layer.

This file used to be a re-export wrapper over the Bagua atomic
operators, but per the v0.6 Atlas-separation doctrine the Yi-flavored
overlay belongs in `Foundation/Atlas/Yi/`.  Until Atlas/Yi grows the
corresponding R₇/R₈ operator surface (Phase γ work-in-progress), this
file remains as a placeholder for the R-index umbrella and does not
re-export anything.
-/
